                <h1>Vivienne Westwood: A Fashion Revolutionary</h1>
                <p>Vivienne Westwood, born in 1941 in England, is a pioneering fashion designer known for her bold and unconventional designs that have challenged norms since the 1970s. She played a key role in the punk fashion movement, merging art and fashion with political activism. Her iconic style continues to influence fashion today.</p>
